name: Logo in toolbar
format:
<script id="clockScript1" type="text/javascript">
    
    var flag;
    var logo = new Image();
    
    
    (function(scope) {
    // watch msg object from Node-RED
    scope.$watch('msg', function(msg) {
        // new message received
        logo.setAttribute('src', msg.payload); 
        });
    })(scope);

    $(function () {
        
        if(flag) return;
        
        //add logo
        var div1 = $('<div/>');
        
        // logo.src = 'data:image/png;base64,'
        logo.height = 70;
        div1[0].style.margin = 'auto 10px auto auto';

        div1.append(logo);

        function addToToolbar() {
            var toolbar = $('.md-toolbar-tools');
            
            if(!toolbar.length) return;
            
            toolbar.append(div1);
            flag = true;
        }
        addToToolbar();
    });
</script>

name: Change the dashboard style (rounded corners)
format:
<style>
/*Change button corner radius (rounded corners)*/
.md-button{             
    border-radius: 10px
}

/*Change card tiles radius (rounded corners)*/
.nr-dashboard-theme ui-card-panel {
    border-radius: 14px;
    border-width: 4px;
}

/*Change style atributes of tile titles (rounded corners)*/
.nr-dashboard-theme ui-card-panel p.nr-dashboard-cardtitle{
    font-size:24px;
    font-weight:bold;
    text-align: center;
    text-shadow: 2px 1px #8c240f;
}


/* Sidebar text changes */
.nr-dashboard-theme md-sidenav div.md-list-item-inner{
  color: rgb(248,64,24)!important;
  
}

/* Change the style of the text in the upper left corner indacting which tab you are on */
.md-toolbar-tools h1{
  font-weight: bold!important;
  text-shadow: 2px 1px #cccccc;
}

.nr-menu-item-active div button{
  background: #4D404040!important;
}


::-webkit-scrollbar {
  width: 10px;
}

/* Track */
::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
  background: #333333;
}
 
/* Handle */
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
  background: #f84018;
  border-radius:10px;
}

/* Handle on hover */
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
  background: #ad2405;
}

#SYSTEM_POWER_cards{
  font-size:20px !important;
}

</style>
